quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,164,"Mu by’ukuri, mu iremwa ry’ibirere n’isi, kubisikana kw’ijoro n’amanywa, amato agenda mu nyanja mu bifitiye abantu akamaro, amazi Allah amanura mu kirere (imvura) nuko akayahesha isi ubuzima nyuma yo gupfa (gukakara) kwayo, akanayikwizamo inyamaswa z’amoko yose, n’ihindagurika ry’imiyaga n’ibicu bigenzwa hagati y’ikirere n’isi; rwose ibyo ni ibimenyetso (bigaragaza ubumwe bw’Imana, ubushobozi n’ingabire byayo) ku bantu bafite ubwenge.",""
  2,165,"No mu bantu hari abishyiriraho ibigirwamana mu cyimbo cya Allah, bakabikunda urukundo nk’urwo bakunda Allah. Nyamara abemera bakunda Allah kurushaho. Kandi abakoze ibibi (imitima yabo babangikanya Allah) iyo baza kumenya -ubwo bazaba babona ibihano (ku munsi w’imperuka)- ko imbaraga zose ari iza Allah kandi ko mu by’ukuri, Allah ari Nyiribihano bikaze (ntibari kubangikanya Allah).",""
  2,166,"Ubwo abakurikiwe bazihakana ababakurikiye (mu kubangikanya Allah), nibamara kubona ibihano, ibyabahuzaga bizavaho.",""
  2,167,"Na ba bandi bakurikiye (ababayobeje) bazavuga bati “Iyaba twari dufite uko twagaruka (ku isi) maze ngo tubihakane nk’uko na bo batwihakanye.” Nguko uko Allah azabereka ibikorwa byabo bibe agahinda kuri bo (ndetse no kwicuza), kandi ntibazava mu muriro.",""
  2,168,"Yemwe bantu! Nimurye mu biri ku isi byaziruwe kandi byiza, ntimuzanakurikire inzira za Shitani. Mu by’ukuri, yo ni umwanzi wanyu ugaragara.",""
  2,169,"Mu by’ukuri, ibategeka ibibi, ibikozasoni no guhimbira Allah ibyo mutazi.",""
